# Intentionally ship the shared Vultr key with the extension so it works out of
# the box for everyone. Negation keeps .env in the package even if a future
# broad ignore pattern would otherwise drop it. Packaging still needs the
# --allow-package-env-file --allow-package-all-secrets flags (see README).
!.env
